### 2. Step-by-Step GitHub Upload Guide

#### Step A: Create a `.gitignore`
Before you upload, you **must** prevent your private API keys and temporary files from going public. Create a file named `.gitignore` in your root:

```text
.env
venv/
__pycache__/
*.mp3
.streamlit/config.toml (optional - keep if you want others to see your theme)